==English==
===Noun===
'''[[aspect]] [[ratio]]'''
{{wikipedia}}
# The ratio of an object's longest [[dimension]] to its next-longest dimension.
# The ratio of width to height in a flat surface or 2-dimensional abstract construction, such as an [[image]], [[character]], or [[pixel]].  4:3 (or 1.33:1) is the standard ratio for [[NTSC]] [[video]].

